        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="subtitle" value="Components grouped by major system, with the architecture mechanisms that span them shown along the bottom. Each component appears as a paragraph in section 2 of architecture-blueprint.md." style="text;html=1;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=11;fontStyle=2;" vertex="1" parent="1">
